description: Build a markov model of everything Hubot hears for each user.
readme:
# Hubot Per-User Markov Model

A fork of [smashwilson/hubot-markov](https://github.com/smashwilson/hubot-markov/) that generates a Markov model for each user in your chat organization based on their speech habits.
